text: cng klaw theid (muhammad) wa thæcring sing thi phracea khxng chanth rng ham nan khux brrda sing chawcha na rangkeiyc thang pen sing thi peidphey cak man læa sing thi mi peidphey læa sing thi pen bap læa kar khmheng rangkæ doy mi pen thrrm læa kar thi phwk cea hı pen pha khi kæ xallxhˌ sung sing thi phraxngkh midi thrng prathan hlakthan dı «lng ma kæ sing nan læa kar thi phwk cea klaw hıray kæ xallxh nı sing thi phwk cea miru
